{"tid":858922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：我撐廣東話-若「粵教中」失優勢也不代表要轉「普教中」","createTime":"2018-10-12T06:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:19:36.000Z","uid":112146,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5061f8b28009e1524266105af1296191fd8c567","tid":858922,"uid":112146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:51:59.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄早前因提出「用廣東話學中文是否能夠長遠？會否令我們失去優勢呢」的言論惹來爭議，其後多次澄清無意貶低廣東話。楊潤雄在一個電台節目中，多次表明「我是撐廣東話」。他又強調，在現行政策下，並無既定要求學校「粵教中」或「普教中」，學校可按教師普通話程度、學生學習能力及專業配套，自行決定用哪種語言教學。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄指，作為教育局長，他認為廣東話、普通話及英語對香港來說「同樣重要」，且並非對立。他說，港人懂廣東話在理解古文上是比內地人有優勢，但普通話同樣重要，若港人到內地發展，懂普通話可方便溝通。他續說，世界上很少地方使用廣東話學中文是事實，香港用廣東話教學會否失去優勢這議題需要研究，但若研究結果顯示會失去優勢，也並不代表香港一定要轉為「普教中」，或者可在其他地方彌補，自己則並無立場，但指這個議題政治化了，已非只是教學問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%92%90%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E8%8B%A5%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%B5%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D%E5%A4%B1%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%A6%81%E8%BD%89%E3%80%8C%E6%99%AE%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D-145611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258B%25A2%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25BD%2589%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E3%2580%258D-145611&d=6JrVqrMZ%2BG20ESSJulJ3SIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d2a848c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%92%90%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E8%8B%A5%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%B5%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D%E5%A4%B1%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%A6%81%E8%BD%89%E3%80%8C%E6%99%AE%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D-145611</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁即係點. 係唔係用英文教?"},{"pid":"4ee2646a1342d9db37cee629b7568be02214f13a","tid":858922,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"用英文教中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b06258f37232d3c0a2d9a46bf5532531a8eda97","tid":858922,"uid":160537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦楊潤雄<br />\n你自己都講緊廣東話㗎<br />\n等天收啦你"},{"pid":"5ff5952d50b206e862e1f0e97737b863077b3b92","tid":858922,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"食屎啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}